(The team=E2=80=99s next home game isn=E2=80=99t until January 20.) The Cli=
ppers, who play in the brand-new Intuit Dome in largely unscathed Inglewood=
, have a Saturday game scheduled against the Hornets, as well.=C2=A0<br/><b=
r/>Meanwhile, all eyes are on the NFL. The Rams=E2=80=99 scheduled playoff =
