=9D As Eriq explained on <em>The Varsity</em> podcast this week, the key is=
 whether the incoming <strong>Trump</strong> administration pursues the cas=
e. =E2=80=9CWith the kind of flux involved, and the different priorities, t=
he new administration might not get involved,=E2=80=9D Eriq noted.<br/><br/=
